@ihunter download current repo, and replace _internal\DeepFaceLab folder.
or download last version from google drive

so it is not just AMD. Getting the same error on a Colab K80 and my own 8GB 1070, so it is not just AMD cards. Test input is a 1080p TV show. 

I do not get the DFL extraction error when the source images of smaller resolutions. My test group for that was pre-extracted 256x256 images from deepfakes/faceswap targeting the same clip. It worked fine.
